w.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/damon-albarn-africa-express-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/damon-albarn-africa-express-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/damon-albarn-africa-express-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>本周末，<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/damon-albarn">达蒙·阿尔巴恩 (Damon Albarn)</a>在墨西哥城的舞台上与他的非洲快报 (Africa Express) 乐队一起翻唱了<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-smiths">史密斯乐队</a>(The Smiths) 的歌曲《Panic》。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/damon-albarns-africa-express-live-collaboration-diversity-brexit-day-2469183">达蒙·阿尔巴恩 (Damon Albarn) 的《非洲快车》现场直播：在本应是英国脱欧日的多元化合作</a></strong></li></ul><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/blur">Blur</a>主唱于周六（2 月 17 日）参加了在墨西哥莫雷洛斯州巴希多拉音乐节 (Bahidorá Festival) 的演出。</p><p>该音乐团体成立于 2006 年，旨在将来自不同文化和音乐流派的艺术家聚集在一起开展合作活动。</p><p> Albarn 在这场充满活力的表演中演唱并弹奏钢琴，Camilo Lara 也加入了对 The Smiths 1986 年歌曲的生动的斯卡演绎。</p><p>查看下面的展示片段。 </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="非洲快车英尺。墨西哥声音研究所 - 恐慌！ （史密斯封面）Bahidora 2024" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/aa15xP5sa7w?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p>上个月宣布演出时，这位<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/gorillaz">Gorillaz</a>艺术家表示，此次演出将标志着 Africa Express 首次访问墨西哥，来自世界各地的音乐家、歌手和 DJ 齐聚一堂，“合作打造一场非常特别、完全原创的演出”。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/damon-albarns-africa-express-live-collaboration-diversity-brexit-day-2469183"><em>《NME》</em>在 2019 年观看了《非洲快报》的现场直播</a>，并以五星级评价将该节目描述为“多样性、协作和团结的象征性展示”。它补充道：“非洲快车很少聚在一起，但一旦聚在一起，它就会专门通过独特的组合创造一次性的时刻。”</p><p>该团体的最后一张专辑《 <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/africa-express-engoli-album-review-2526291">Egoli</a> 》也于 2019 年发行。 <em>NME</em><a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/africa-express-engoli-album-review-2526291">在四星评论中</a>写道：“这张由 Damon Albarn、Gruff Rhys、Moonchild Sanelly 等人主演的合作唱片是一部漫无目的、享乐主义的日记。这是该集体迄今为止最好的作品。” </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/C2P2zDKITfO/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 60px;"></div></div></div><div style="padding: 19% 0;"></div><div style="display:block; height:50px; margin:0 auto 12px; width:50px;"><svg width="50px" height="50px" viewBox="0 0 60 60" version="1.1" xmlns="https://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="https://www.w3.org/1999/xlink"><g stroke="none" stroke-width="1" fill="none" fill-rule="evenodd"><g transform="translate(-511.000000, -20.000000)" fill="#000000"><g><path d="M556.869,30.41 C554.814,30.41 553.148,32.076 553.148,34.131 C553.148,36.186 554.814,37.852 556.869,37.852 C558.924,37.852 560.59,36.186 560.59,34.131 C560.59,32.076 558.924,30.41 556.869,30.41 M541,60.657 C535.114,60.657 530.342,55.887 530.342,50 C530.342,44.114 535.114,39.342 541,39.342 C546.887,39.342 551.658,44.114 551.658,50 C551.658,55.887 546.887,60.657 541,60.657 M541,33.886 C532.1,33.886 524.886,41.1 524.886,50 C524.886,58.899 532.1,66.113 541,66.113 C549.9,66.113 557.115,58.899 557.115,50 C557.115,41.1 549.9,33.886 541,33.886 M565.378,62.101 C565.244,65.022 564.756,66.606 564.346,67.663 C563.803,